{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-property-unit-blacklist/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-block-no-redundant-longhand-properties/","description":"declaration-no-important 禁止声明的 !important。 如果您期望总是使用 !important，例如您正在编写用户样式，您可以使用postcss-safe-important安全的添加。 选项 true 以下模式被视为违规： 以下模式不被视为违规：","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"declaration-no-important\"><a href=\"#declaration-no-important\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>declaration-no-important</h1>\n<p>禁止声明的 <code>!important</code>。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink <span class=\"hljs-meta\">!important</span>; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**             ↑\n * 这个 !important */</span></code></pre>\n<p>如果您期望总是使用 <code>!important</code>，例如您正在编写<a href=\"https://userstyles.org/\">用户样式</a>，您可以使用<a href=\"https://github.com/crimx/postcss-safe-important\"><code>postcss-safe-important</code></a><em>安全的</em>添加。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<h3 id=\"true\"><a href=\"#true\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>true</code></h3>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink <span class=\"hljs-meta\">!important</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink ! important; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink<span class=\"hljs-meta\">!important</span>; }</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/declaration-no-important.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-no-important/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-no-important/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-no-important/index.html.4ff52bcb32942811fedac9c56e11b8c6.json"}